cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.CV

This paper is about machine learning algorithms, specifically Gradient Boosting Decision Tree (GBDT), and how to optimize its training process using Parameter Server. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CV (Computer Vision) as GBDT is often used in computer vision tasks.
